ript></p><p>一日活动门票现已发售，价格为 45 英镑（成人）和 20 英镑（儿童）—— <a href="https://www.seetickets.com/event/pilton-party/worthy-farm/3079784" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里购买</a>。查看上面的官方阵容海报。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-streets-and-arlo-parks-to-play-glastonburys-pilton-party-2023-3478597">去年的皮尔顿派对 (Pilton Party) 举办了 The Streets 和 Arlo Parks 的表演</a>。最近参与该法案的其他乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elbow-and-easy-life-announced-for-glastonburys-pilton-party-3283579">Elbow、Hard Life（原名 Easy Life）</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wolf-alice-headline-glastonburys-pilton-party-2533776">Wolf Alice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/supergrass">Supergrass</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supergrass-reunite-to-play-glastonburys-annual-pilton-party-2545720">于 2019 年在活动中重聚</a>）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a> 。</p><p> 2020 年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-martin">克里斯·马丁 (Chris Martin)</a>回忆<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chris-martin-filling-in-the-strokes-coldplay-headlining-glastonbury-2002-2696924">起酷玩乐队 (Coldplay) 在皮尔顿派对 (Pilton Party) 上替代 The Strokes 后，如何让他的乐队在格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 (Glastonbury Festival) 上首次登上头条</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/coldplay-glastonbury-2024-live-review-photos-setlist-3770486">马丁和他的同事们六月重返沃西农场，第五次打破纪录登上金字塔舞台</a>。他们与<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/dua-lipa-live-at-glastonbury-2024-review-setlist-photos-3770003">Dua Lipa</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/sza-live-at-glastonbury-2024-setlist-review-photos-3770784">SZA</a>一起登上了 2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的榜首。</p><p>现在，所有人的目光都集中在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2025-dates-tickets-price-line-up-when-on-sale-3771375">2025 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上</a>，该音乐节将于 6 月 25 日星期三至 6 月 29 日星期日举行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/emily-eavis-confirms-glastonbury-fallow-year-2026-in-talks-with-acts-for-2025-3770919">2026 年将是休耕年</a>。下一届的门票预计将于 11 月开始发售，然后在春季重新发售。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="浪荡子乐队在《东方滨海艺术中心一切安静》中谈论清洁和联系" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CtuPJQWz_mQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/glastonbury-2025-headliners-rumours-3773153">关于 2025 年潜在头条新闻的谣言已经在流传</a>，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">萨姆·芬德 (Sam Fender)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">绿日乐队 (Green Day)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队 (The Rolling Stones)</a> 。然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-respond-to-glastonbury-2025-rumours-and-the-chances-of-other-festivals-3788269#:~:text=Now%2C%20Oasis%20have%20responded%20to,next%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20began.">最近改革的绿洲乐队已经排除了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-tickets-faq-buy-when-how-much-3789123">明年夏天大型重聚巡演</a>的一部分。</p><p>与此同时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cher-reportedly-in-talks-for-legends-slot-at-glastonbury-2025-3790138">据报道，雪儿正在就 2025 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上令人垂涎的传奇人物席位进行“谈判”</a> 。</p><p>在其他消息中，CMAT 因其广受好评的第二张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/cmat-crazymad-for-me-review-lyrics-tracklist-3512398">“Crazymad，For Me”而</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cmat-mercury-prize-interview-charli-xcx-corinne-bailey-rae-latitude-boycott-gaza-israel-3778326">获得今年水星奖的提名</a>。 2024 年奖项的获奖者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-tv-and-radio-programme-announced-3785881">将于明天（9 月 5 日）在 Abbey Road Studios 现场揭晓</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-and-cmat-to-play-glastonburys-pilton-party-this-weekend-3790498">The Libertines 和 CMAT 本周末将参加 Glastonbury 的 Pilton Party 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a hre